# Fluff Date: 2026-03-18 15:07:44
<overview>
<p>Conventional infantry within the DCMS serve as the foundation of planetary defense, providing the manpower essential to territorial control while freeing BattleMech and armored assets for offensive operations. The platoon tows a light autocannon that balances range and hitting power, capable of threatening armored vehicles at distances that keep the gun crew clear of direct infantry engagement. A versatile field piece that earns its place in any garrison defense plan.</p>
</overview>

